,{"pid":"b01ad98e5c087567b76efe4a494a29e4de28eb71","tid":2087381,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:16:07.000Z","msg":"恐怖平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d57a653a60233f8e4bfaa8148b0166f36ae9661","tid":2087381,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:19:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7d6ef8af0327ed1965807eb73283bd7080d74a","tid":2087381,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:20:33.000Z","msg":"「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"e752210b868adcaa8a5bd0b85c46842636179bc5","tid":2087381,"uid":267395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:21:28.000Z","msg":"你每下呼吸你都搶緊國家既空氣 係仇視國家既行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />槍斃"},{"pid":"609362472cfd4014737e4fb731c05d4648f01476","tid":2087381,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:22:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔怪得 3/7 派一萬蚊啦  <br />\n明哂</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}